{"tid":285644,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"拍出「最爛蝙蝠俠電影」導演20年後道歉了","createTime":"2017-06-16T04:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T07:17:47.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57bb6aea9162b11fb974f6abc3cb287d8babfab6","tid":285644,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"1997年上映的《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》（Batman &amp; Robin），被大多數影迷認為是最差的蝙蝠俠電影，至今年剛好滿20年，導演喬伊舒麥雪（Joel Schumacher）近來受訪時首度對造成粉絲失望表達歉意，強調「都是我的錯」，並解釋為何在裡頭的蝙蝠裝設計了「奶頭」，解除大家疑問。"},{"pid":"423b45a2d0fe5c44bd8bd641087d0dc015331b5a","tid":285644,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"《蝙蝠俠3》1995年上映後創下超高票房，但是方基墨（Val Kilmer）卻為了拍《The Island of Dr. Moreau》不願意接演《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》，最後便找來當時正紅的喬治克隆尼（George Clooney）飾演蝙蝠俠，還找來鄔瑪舒曼（Uma Thurman）和阿諾史瓦辛格（Arnold Schwarzenegger）演反派，大咖雲集，華納也對新的男主角相當滿意，沒想到最後票房評價滑鐵盧，混亂的劇情、角色設定和造型都被影迷罵翻，喬治克隆尼之後也常以此自嘲。"},{"pid":"f088ca9fd9af985160e588a896bb7c793e626a75","tid":285644,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"據《Vice》報導，喬伊舒麥雪對於搞砸這部電影表示：「我就好像親手殺死一個小孩，這大部分都是我自己的選擇，其他人不用負責，只有我除外。」了解觀眾在《蝙蝠俠3》後對接下來的作品抱有很大的期待，結果在《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》後評論卻變得很嚴厲。"},{"pid":"a4ac8c3be5e255acbb128aa35850c9b6345880ff","tid":285644,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"被問到為什麼蝙蝠俠的戰袍在這集換上了乳頭，喬伊舒麥雪表示，這想法來自於荷西費南德茲（Jose Fernandez），對比早期幾部的服裝，《蝙蝠俠3》和《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》的橡膠技術已經不同，即使米高基頓（Michael Keaton ）穿的尺寸很大，還是很棒的作品，而且在當時已經是最好的，但是到了《蝙蝠俠4：急凍人》，橡膠衣的製作更進步，所以當時就提供一些希臘的神像、醫學書籍做參考，荷西就這樣做出了奶頭，而他也覺得這個造型很酷，沒想到觀眾不買單。"},{"pid":"c1b886a12e659d65fdf454a9f0086e9f9391e7b7","tid":285644,"uid":2380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"細個成日係明珠台睇呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個毒藤女周街咀人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 羅賓要痴膠紙落咀到"},{"pid":"ebb9d6b4c29b30b238007bf4b2c594d36c9ad372","tid":285644,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"奶頭裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4870590dd35fde9827064306790ce7f059045a","tid":285644,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶頭裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沒想到觀眾不買單"},{"pid":"0febdeca9d35f8a84705ddf8f6119df8cd870c41","tid":285644,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"Alicia Silverstone <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c933cdf0960ecb0dfaccb0c47b9284a0d3d69e","tid":285644,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"想睇由添布頓拍晒幾部曲會點"},{"pid":"5533e7a750151c0d856f30118fb9dd0d6418c5c8","tid":285644,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"舊版batman先係真batman<br />\n<br />\n路蘭拍既唔可以叫batman"},{"pid":"26508e97b6a67224d48533531ac21280b0e8083d","tid":285644,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"係咪batman冇啦啦拎張visa出嚟嗰套?"},{"pid":"5dcdedd46fc4793310907084c5892c201101aab3","tid":285644,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪batman冇啦啦拎張visa出嚟嗰套?</blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"b29312ba9f50c0f1395dde60964e3be72